| 步骤                                                  | 描述                                                         |
| ----------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| WifiConfStepCode.WIFI_CONF_START                      | 开始配网                                                     |
| WifiConfStepCode.PROTOCOL_START                       | 配网协议开始                                                 |
| WifiConfStepCode.CONNECT_SOFTAP_START                 | 开始连接设备热点                                             |
